      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see some inconsistency between the prefixes `pldm_rde_` and `pldm_rde_rde_`\n\nExample\n```\npldm_rde_rde_operation_init_req\n\nPLDM_RDE_OPERATION_INIT_RESP_FIXED_BYTES\n```",
